overview: Kira Noir enters Jade Baker's bedroom where she lies on the bed looking miserable, surrounded by tissues and food wrappers. Kira assures her that she doesn't need her ex to have fun in bed. Kenzie Taylor thinks that Serena Blair is going to make a fuss out of her being a lesbian, though it's revealed that she is actually trying to make a big deal out of her love of anal sex.
tagline: Just like her boyfriend used to...
title: In Love with Anal Sex
